            <section ID="Lf389a937-d860-4d1c-bdc6-e8c70c42e9a2">
               <id root="5ea8a4ac-2df6-455a-b87d-97f97cb3c348"/>
               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Identity</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>No. 1000, GLOFIL-125 is a clear, colorless, sterile, and nonpyrogenic solution available as a 4 mL vial. It is supplied in a concentration of approximately 1 mg/mL sodium iothalamate (range is 0.5–2.0 mg sodium iothalamate per mL), with a radioactivity concentration of 250 to 300 μCi/mL at the time of calibration. Benzyl alcohol 0.9%, is added as a preservative. Sodium bicarbonate and hydrochloric acid are added for pH adjustment. The calibration and expiration dates are shown on the label.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20191213"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="Le94f22c2-4052-4ecb-be82-a329aa7eb4e7">
               <id root="1429fc64-52c2-4a66-b32d-3670fec45f79"/>
               <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold">Storage</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Refrigerate the product upon receipt at 2°C to 8°C.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20140411"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="L66c4a344-e21f-4e8b-827b-ec9647159a09">
